  const getErrorsHandled = (
    nameProductValue,
    slugProductValue,
    originalPriceProductValue,
    sellingPriceProductValue,
    quantityProductValue,
    imageProductValue,
    metaTitleProductValue,   
    smallDescriptionProductValue,
    descriptionProductValue,
    metaDescriptionProductValue,
    metaKeywordProductValue
  ) => {
    if (
      nameProductValue === "" &&
      slugProductValue === "" &&
      originalPriceProductValue === "" &&
      sellingPriceProductValue === "" &&
      quantityProductValue === "" &&
      metaTitleProductValue === "" &&
      smallDescriptionProductValue === "" &&
      descriptionProductValue === "" &&
      metaDescriptionProductValue === "" &&
      metaKeywordProductValue === ""
    ) {
      return {
        message:
          "Vous devez obligatoirement remplir les champs vides",
        elements: [
          [
            nameProduct,
            slugProduct,
            original_priceProduct,
            selling_priceProduct,
            quantityProduct,
            meta_titleProduct,
            small_descriptionProduct,
            descriptionProduct,
            meta_descriptionProduct,
            meta_keywordProduct,
          ],
        ],
      };
    } else {
      if (
        getErrors(
          nameProductValue,
          slugProductValue,
          originalPriceProductValue,
          sellingPriceProductValue,
          quantityProductValue,
          imageProductValue,
          metaTitleProductValue,          
          smallDescriptionProductValue,
          descriptionProductValue,
          metaDescriptionProductValue,
          metaKeywordProductValue
        ).nameProductError !== "" &&
        getErrors(
          nameProductValue,
          slugProductValue,
          originalPriceProductValue,
          sellingPriceProductValue,
          quantityProductValue,
          imageProductValue,
          metaTitleProductValue,         
          smallDescriptionProductValue,
          descriptionProductValue,
          metaDescriptionProductValue,

          smallDescriptionProductValue === "" &&
          descriptionProductValue !== "" &&
          metaDescriptionProductValue === "" &&
          metaKeywordProductValue !== ""
        ) {
          let elts = [
            nameProduct,
            slugProduct,
            meta_titleProduct,
            original_priceProduct,
            selling_priceProduct,
            quantityProduct,
            imageProduct,
            select,
            small_descriptionProduct,
            meta_descriptionProduct,
          ];

          array.push(elts);
        } else if (
          smallDescriptionProductValue === "" &&
          descriptionProductValue === "" &&
          metaDescriptionProductValue !== "" &&
          metaKeywordProductValue !== ""
        ) {
          let elts = [

        ) {

          ];

        } else if (

          metaKeywordProductValue !== ""
        ) {
          let elts = [
            nameProduct,
            slugProduct,

            original_priceProduct,
            selling_priceProduct,

            imageProduct,
            select,
            descriptionProduct,
          ];

          array.push(elts);
        } else if (
          smallDescriptionProductValue === "" &&
          descriptionProductValue !== "" &&
          metaDescriptionProductValue !== "" &&
          metaKeywordProductValue !== ""
        ) {
          let elts = [
            nameProduct,
            slugProduct,
            meta_titleProduct,
            original_priceProduct,
            selling_priceProduct,
            quantityProduct,
            imageProduct,
            select,
            small_descriptionProduct,
          ];

          array.push(elts);
        } else {
          let elts = [
            nameProduct,
            slugProduct,
            meta_titleProduct,
            original_priceProduct,
            selling_priceProduct,
            quantityProduct,
            imageProduct,
            select,
          ];

          array.push(elts);
        }

        return {
          message:
            "Les champs nom, slug et titre possdent des caractres invalides(seules les lettres sont autorises),les champs prix de depart, de vente et quantit possdent des caractres invalides (seuls les chiffres sont autoriss),l'image que vous avez fourni possde une extension non valide(les extensions autorises sont .jpg, .JPG, .jpeg, .JPEG, .png, .PNG) et veuillez selectionner une catgorie pour ce produit",

          elements: array,
        };
      } else {
        let array = [];
        let messageErreur = "";

        if (
          smallDescriptionProductValue === "" &&
          descriptionProductValue === "" &&
          metaDescriptionProductValue === "" &&
          metaKeywordProductValue === ""
        ) {
          let elts = [
            small_descriptionProduct,
            descriptionProduct,
            meta_descriptionProduct,
            meta_keywordProduct,
          ];

          messageErreur = "Veuillez obligatoirement remplir les champs vides";

          array.push(elts);
        } else if (
          smallDescriptionProductValue !== "" &&
          descriptionProductValue === "" &&
          metaDescriptionProductValue === "" &&
          metaKeywordProductValue === ""
        ) {

            descriptionProduct,

          ];

        ) {
